//www.lifeprint.com/asl101/topics/signlanguagediversity3.htm%0a%3c %0a%3c [2] http://www.deaflibrary.org/jsl.html%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c (:Category:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
